                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000ef84ae16-3137-4cc9-bede-528fbe6c50e4" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(s=\frac{1}{2}a{t}^{2}⇒a=\frac{2s}{{t}^{2}}=1.6\ ft{s}^{-2}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001ef84ae16-3137-4cc9-bede-528fbe6c50e4"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000ef84ae16-3137-4cc9-bede-528fbe6c50e4 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001ef84ae16-3137-4cc9-bede-528fbe6c50e4 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000008e49f918-0dff-4ddc-98ea-04ea86ac7a7a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴F-{f}_{k}=ma⇒45\ g-μmg=ma\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000018e49f918-0dff-4ddc-98ea-04ea86ac7a7a"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000008e49f918-0dff-4ddc-98ea-04ea86ac7a7a {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000018e49f918-0dff-4ddc-98ea-04ea86ac7a7a {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000009ba689ea-2b31-409c-9b2d-07636701a856" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒μ=\frac{45\ g-ma}{mg}=\frac{45\times 32-100\times 1.6}{100\times 32}=0.4\ \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000019ba689ea-2b31-409c-9b2d-07636701a856"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000009ba689ea-2b31-409c-9b2d-07636701a856 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000019ba689ea-2b31-409c-9b2d-07636701a856 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;p