                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000156d4700-ecc2-4d5c-b61d-07260e9c4928" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(ln\ \left(\frac{{C}_{2}}{{C}_{1}}\right)=-\frac{ln(2)}{{T}_{\frac{1}{2}}}t\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001156d4700-ecc2-4d5c-b61d-07260e9c4928"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000156d4700-ecc2-4d5c-b61d-07260e9c4928 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001156d4700-ecc2-4d5c-b61d-07260e9c4928 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000544c5599-0541-46dc-bdd7-2fcf6ad27a1f" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(ln\ {\left(\frac{0.5}{2}\right)=-\left(\frac{ln\ {2}}{{T}_{\frac{1}{2}}}\right)t}⇒{T}_{\frac{1}{2}}\times ln\ {\left(\frac{1}{4}\right)}=-ln\ {\left(2\right)\times t}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001544c5599-0541-46dc-bdd7-2fcf6ad27a1f"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000544c5599-0541-46dc-bdd7-2fcf6ad27a1f {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001544c5599-0541-46dc-bdd7-2fcf6ad27a1f {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000d5b4f7fd-18ff-4a48-b756-9bdfb6d2ecf3" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒{T}_{\frac{1}{2}}\times \left(-2\right)\times \left(ln\ {2}\right)=-ln\ {\left(2\right)\times t}\ ⇒t=2\times {T}_{\frac{1}{2}}⇒t=120\ sec.\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001d5b4f7fd-18ff-4a48-b756-9bdfb6d2ecf3"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000d5b4f7fd-18ff-4a48-b756-9bdfb6d2ecf3 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001d5b4f7fd-18ff-4a48-b756-9bdfb6d2ecf3 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000061b308d2-fd3f-4416-bc4c-0d99f40729a5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000161b308d2-fd3f-4416-bc4c-0d99f40729a5">weK&#237; c&#215;wZ: </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({T}_{\frac{1}{2}}=60\ sec\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000261b308d2-fd3f-4416-bc4c-0d99f40729a5">; </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{1}{4}=\frac{1}{{2}^{2}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000261b308d2-fd3f-4416-bc4c-0d99f40729a5"> </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000361b308d2-fd3f-4416-bc4c-0d99f40729a5">fvM n‡Z c&#214;‡qvRbxq mgq </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=\left({T}_{\frac{1}{2}}\right)\times 2=60\times 2\ sec=120\ sec.\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000061b308d2-fd3f-4416-bc4c-0d99f40729a5 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000161b308d2-fd3f-4416-bc4c-0d99f40729a5 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-00000261b308d2-fd3f-4416-bc4c-0d99f40729a5 {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-00000361b308d2-fd3f-4416-bc4c-0d99f40729a5 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
