                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000008484a8a3-1e3b-4bee-9df2-dbf832b6263c" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\underset{x→0}{lim}\frac{1-{e}^{2x}}{ln\ {\left(1-x\right)}}=\underset{x→0}{lim}\ \frac{-2{e}^{2x}}{\frac{-1}{1-x}}\ \left[ {L}^{{'}\ }H\widehat {o}pital\ Rule\right] \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000018484a8a3-1e3b-4bee-9df2-dbf832b6263c"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=\underset{x→0}{lim}\ \ \left(1-x\right)\left(2{e}^{2x}\right)=2\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000018484a8a3-1e3b-4bee-9df2-dbf832b6263c">  </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000008484a8a3-1e3b-4bee-9df2-dbf832b6263c {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000018484a8a3-1e3b-4bee-9df2-dbf832b6263c {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
