                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000020d01186-5607-4bc9-ab02-761e15390c07" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000120d01186-5607-4bc9-ab02-761e15390c07">[awi, e„nr A</span><span class="pt-00000120d01186-5607-4bc9-ab02-761e15390c07">&#182;</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000120d01186-5607-4bc9-ab02-761e15390c07"> </span><span class="pt-00000220d01186-5607-4bc9-ab02-761e15390c07">x</span><span class="pt-00000120d01186-5607-4bc9-ab02-761e15390c07">-A</span><span class="pt-00000120d01186-5607-4bc9-ab02-761e15390c07">&#182;</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000120d01186-5607-4bc9-ab02-761e15390c07"> eivei]</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000020d01186-5607-4bc9-ab02-761e15390c07 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000120d01186-5607-4bc9-ab02-761e15390c07 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-00000220d01186-5607-4bc9-ab02-761e15390c07 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000a766c13d-c44c-49d8-8614-b9368f4e1b2b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001a766c13d-c44c-49d8-8614-b9368f4e1b2b">c&#214;kœg</span><span class="pt-000001a766c13d-c44c-49d8-8614-b9368f4e1b2b">‡Z,</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002a766c13d-c44c-49d8-8614-b9368f4e1b2b"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{2{b}^{2}}{a}=a⇒\frac{{b}^{2}}{{a}^{2}}=\frac{1}{2}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000003a766c13d-c44c-49d8-8614-b9368f4e1b2b">; </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(e=\sqrt{1-\frac{{b}^{2}}{{a}^{2}}}\ =\sqrt{1-\frac{1}{2}}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\ \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000004a766c13d-c44c-49d8-8614-b9368f4e1b2b"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000a766c13d-c44c-49d8-8614-b9368f4e1b2b {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001a766c13d-c44c-49d8-8614-b9368f4e1b2b {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002a766c13d-c44c-49d8-8614-b9368f4e1b2b {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000003a766c13d-c44c-49d8-8614-b9368f4e1b2b {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000004a766c13d-c44c-49d8-8614-b9368f4e1b2b {font-family: Vrinda;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
