                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000041fdc4fd-a1d8-43b1-ba7a-52f731f71f38" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({sin}^{-1}\ {\frac{1}{2}}=\frac{π}{6}\ ∴cot\ {\left({sin}^{-1}\ {\frac{1}{2}}\right)}=cot\ {\frac{π}{6}=\sqrt{3}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000141fdc4fd-a1d8-43b1-ba7a-52f731f71f38"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000041fdc4fd-a1d8-43b1-ba7a-52f731f71f38 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000141fdc4fd-a1d8-43b1-ba7a-52f731f71f38 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
